Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是關於一對\N感情非常好的姊妹的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.69,0:00:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著同樣的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.83,0:00:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一樣的學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回一樣的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣小小的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.33,0:00:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直持續的悲傷的夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.23,0:00:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間的黃昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.58,0:01:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行著一段永遠的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.49,0:01:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖繼續探索著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.96,0:01:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片發出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.14,0:01:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.38,0:01:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尋找遺失的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.55,0:01:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手的掌心確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.92,0:01:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.26,0:01:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間開始流動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道美阪同學\N生的是什麼病嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.49,0:02:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼病？不是感冒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.49,0:02:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美阪同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「在笑容的背後」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.23,0:02:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有在一年級的開學典禮時\N來過學校一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.96,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有…一次？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.94,0:02:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直都請假沒有來學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞她…是什麼病？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.22,0:02:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞這個女孩子\N我跟你說過我不認識吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又在說那種謊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.49,0:02:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想相澤同學或許不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.43,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在的中庭\N看起來是十分的冷清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.23,0:03:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但當雪溶化\N天氣變得暖和起來時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.97,0:03:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有很多的學生\N而顯得熱鬧起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是午休時間吃便當最棒的場所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在這樣說\N沒什麼說服力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那個叫栞的女孩如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.89,0:03:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在意她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.69,0:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道該怎麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就是無法放著她不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小的…就像妹妹一樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳呢？妳又是怎麼想的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看鬼臉唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有蝴蝶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 來玩嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 祐一\N張嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.61,0:04:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為因為你一直在發呆嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.88,0:04:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 每個人\N都有他自己的喜好唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 這裡是水瀨家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 稍等一下\N真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.76,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是香里打來的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說有話要說…是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是栞的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我妹妹的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.21,0:04:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的妹妹的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過一個禮拜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是她的生日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.89,0:05:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說她\N活不到下一次的生日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她出生後身體就不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.27,0:05:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說大概沒辦法活到\N下次的生日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.21,0:05:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近身體慢慢的好了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定可以迎接\N下個生日的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.13,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…就只有那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都…不會改變…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.87,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞她什麼時候知道的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年的…耶誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.82,0:06:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我…告訴她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她問我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.46,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要當作沒有她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要不在了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.04,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再沒有多久…\N就要從我的眼前消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.58,0:07:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我知道…因為知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…妹妹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果從一開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.65,0:07:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不存在的話就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相澤同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.73,0:07:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是為了什麼\N來到人間呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一想要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且有什麼\N是我可以做得到的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和栞一起渡過快樂的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一堆會心跳加速的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一堆會令人興奮的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓快樂的感覺和高興的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.79,0:08:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,填滿栞的內心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.66,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓她開心的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快樂的…感覺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的病…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是即使吃一堆藥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打一堆針…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也醫不好的病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.99,0:09:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 我有一個請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.09,0:09:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把我當成普通女孩般對待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.46,0:09:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只在到生日為止的\N這一個禮拜之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的…沒有別的辦法了嗎…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生奇跡的話…\N也許還有什麼方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為不會發生…\N所以才叫做奇跡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.29,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以…拜託你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是中庭的那個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.56,0:09:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來她是我們學校的學生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.87,0:09:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我對畫肖像畫很在行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特大綜合水果聖代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算耳朵的大小不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兔子還是兔子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.07,0:10:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來還差的很遠呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.78,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說這種話的人最討厭了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.97,0:10:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和祐一相遇的地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.91,0:10:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得妳拿著糖果啊什麼的\N在發呆著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.04,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一個禮拜…\N我過的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果以連續劇來講…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是哪一幕呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要到完結篇了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.27,0:11:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天…到幾點呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是到午夜12點吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.85,0:11:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起待到\N日期轉換的瞬間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借用點時間…可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是生日禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡畫畫吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以畫祐一嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一頁…我想要畫祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.99,0:12:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了也不能生氣唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我覺得妳不適合畫畫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.38,0:12:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然…是那樣嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.72,0:12:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也有那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我很高興唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說原來我在栞眼裡\N是這副模樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.86,0:12:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很開心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時也有點複雜呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種說法…不太高興呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.33,0:13:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的很高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮的星空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣仰望著天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人覺得時間好像停止了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.73,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時間根本就不可能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來跳舞吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.66,0:14:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是一直都很想參加舞會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡…跳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年的耶誕節…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我送了妹妹披肩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.46,0:14:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那之後病就變得嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為很難過…很害怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒辦法不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.27,0:14:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞還有多少日子可活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.87,0:14:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她卻笑著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.21,0:14:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使已經覺悟到自己的命運…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管自己的身體有多痛苦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.55,0:15:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…越是想要躲開她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.32,0:15:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻原諒了一切…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢地笑著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.77,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明哭出來就好了…\N我是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就直接說出來就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她卻總是一直笑著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…是不是一直笑著的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.93,0:15:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是…做到了一直笑著呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是多虧了祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了堅強的祐一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堅強的是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.09,0:16:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…曾經想過要割腕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.09,0:16:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第一次跟祐一相遇的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.36,0:16:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在商店街買了美工刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到這是最後一次的購物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.94,0:16:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得好像連些不必要的東西\N也一起買了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.11,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…就那樣\N邊欣賞著最後的雪景邊回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在路上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.10,0:16:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…還記得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天的晚上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在關掉了燈的自己房間裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都聽不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都無法思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.42,0:17:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿只有我一個人\N被遺棄在這世上的夜晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.12,0:17:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開被雪弄濕了的紙袋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握著黃色的美工刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露出銀白的刀刃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.87,0:17:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將它貼放在左手腕上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.31,0:17:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我突然聽到了笑聲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.65,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在白天遇到的\N祐一你們的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個笑容…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個看起來很快樂的笑容…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個聽起來很快樂的笑聲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.57,0:18:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到那些…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.87,0:18:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得現在的自己\N是多麼的悲慘…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像被牽動著 笑了起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.02,0:18:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是隔了相當久的笑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己活不到下個生日…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.09,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連姊姊這樣告訴我時\N也沒有流下的淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也流了下來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要忘去她的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.12,0:18:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以她便想讓自己消失…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.76,0:19:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為做不到…\N所以她哭泣了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法停住一直強忍住的眼淚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意到自己正在哭著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我注意到的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.44,0:19:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不再握著美工刀了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.11,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…這個就是奇跡呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很軟弱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.45,0:19:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才將那份軟弱加諸在栞身上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為妳很堅強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那種事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是軟弱的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.64,0:19:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不被他人拯救\N就無法活下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.78,0:19:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的軟弱的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.28,0:19:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也沒有什麼不好 不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.88,0:20:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不論是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.52,0:20:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不能不依靠他人活下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡這種東西啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為有那麼一點\N小小的發生的可能性…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫做奇跡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.30,0:20:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生的…可能性…\N即使只有一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.79,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上同樣的制服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.56,0:20:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起從家裡去同樣的學校…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.39,0:20:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是這樣約好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是只是妳的夢想而已呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的夢想呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊…夢想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿同樣的制服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.35,0:21:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的學校…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.55,0:21:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里 一起去百貨公司吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.44,0:21:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 今天不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在急什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.21,0:21:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹…栞在醫院等我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得不太跟我們一起玩了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.18,0:21:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為香里看起來\N比以前更開心了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.02,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.19,0:21:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.12,0:21:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來接你了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以買肉包給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.29,0:21:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別靠那麼近 熱死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.13,0:21:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很熱呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.57,0:21:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.47,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要買肉包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.34,0:22:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.47,0:22:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買啦 買啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.98,0:22:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是小孩子啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說別靠那麼近啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.25,0:22:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉包子\N熱死了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.16,0:22:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從隨風飄流的雲朵之間\N窺視到晴空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.24,0:22:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連熟悉的街道也閃閃發光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.52,0:22:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前奔跑的小小的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.76,0:22:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.80,0:23:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用天真來蓋過溢出的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.54,0:23:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間靜悄悄的流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.72,0:23:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吹拂著溫柔的風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.82,0:23:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為凍僵的思念也會化做笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.30,0:23:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真琴倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.44,0:23:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在束手無策的我的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.64,0:23:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神秘少女美汐出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.48,0:23:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanon第10話\N冬天的煙火
